    has 2 or more Digimon, reduce the play cost by 5.\n[On Play] [When Digivolving]
    Return all of your opponent's Digimon with the fewest digivolution cards to the
    bottom of the deck.\n[All Turns] [Once Per Turn] When this Digimon suspends,
    it may unsuspend.\n[All Turns] When any of your Digimon with the [TS]\_trait
    or [Aqua] or [Sea Animal]\_in any of their traits would leave the battle area
    by your opponent's effects, by suspending this Digimon, they don't leave."
